{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WorkerGlobalScope: languagechange イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>console</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/location\"><code>location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/navigator\"><code>navigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>self</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/dump\"><code>dump()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts\"><code>importScripts()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>languagechange</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/offline_event\"><code>offline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/online_event\"><code>online</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>languagechange</code></strong> イベントはグローバルスコープオブジェクトで、ユーザーの推奨言語が変更されたときに発生します。</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">バブリング</th>\n   <td>なし</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル</th>\n   <td>不可</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラー</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event\"><code>onlanguagechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>languagechange</code> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener</code></a> メソッドで使用することができます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>worker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange event detected!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>または、 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event\"><code>onlanguagechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> イベントハンドラープロパティを使用することもできます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>worker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onlanguagechange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange event detected!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/workers.html#the-workerglobalscope-common-interface:event-languagechange\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">languagechange の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.WorkerGlobalScope.languagechange_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/language\" title=\"navigator.language\"><code>navigator.language</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/languages\" title=\"navigator.languages\"><code>navigator.languages</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.onlanguagechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"languagechange イベントはグローバルスコープオブジェクトで、ユーザーの推奨言語が変更されたときに発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WorkerGlobalScope: languagechange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WorkerGlobalScope.onlanguagechange","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/workerglobalscope/languagechange_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/workerglobalscope/languagechange_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope","title":"WorkerGlobalScope"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event","title":"WorkerGlobalScope: languagechange イベント"}],"pa